## Retake Policy
- **Cooling-off Period:** None (can retake immediately)
- **Validity Period:** Both exams must be passed within 3 years
- **Score Validity:** Individual exam scores valid for 2 years
- **Failed Exam Retakes:** Pay full fee for retake

---

## Certification Validity & Renewal

### CompTIA A+ Validity
- **Initial Certification Period:** 3 years from passing both exams
- **Renewal Requirements:**
  - Take and pass a new CompTIA A+ exam, OR
  - Earn a higher-level CompTIA certification (Network+, Security+, etc.), OR
  - Participate in CompTIA Continuing Education program

### CEU (Continuing Education Units)
- **Available Through:** CompTIA training partners
- **Credits Needed:** 20 CEUs to renew
- **Cost:** Varies ($0-200 depending on method)

